    "description_long": "This is a large, modern fire truck painted in a vibrant red color with white and silver accents. The vehicle features prominent emergency lights on the roof and sides, as well as a pair of ladders securely mounted on the top. The sides display detailed graphics of firefighting equipment and branding, including the words 'SAMFlows' and 'IDX Fire & Safety.' The rear of the truck has a visible ladder for roof access and additional emergency markings. The cab is spacious, with large windows for visibility, and the body is constructed from sturdy metal panels. The wheels are robust, designed for heavy-duty urban and emergency use.",
